and wave equation?

00:01:43.220 --> 00:01:51.020
So I'll say heat
versus wave equations.

00:01:51.020 --> 00:01:55.000
What are the sort of
biggest differences?

00:01:55.000 --> 00:02:05.550
The heat, the signal
travels infinitely fast.

00:02:11.390 --> 00:02:15.170
